headline: UP, Norfolk Southern Push Back on Class I Challenges to Merger Filing
summary: The railroads say competitors’ objections are “baseless” and improperly argue the merits rather than the completeness of the filing.

headline: 1 Profitable Stock to Target This Week and 2 We Brush Off
summary: Even if a company is profitable, it doesn’t always mean it’s a great investment. Some struggle to maintain growth, face looming threats, or fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their future potential.
